snippet.textDisplay:
My family has been rewatching the original trilogy and honestly, Yoda doesn't really switch words around that much. There's the occasional "I am/have" and "you are/have" thrown at the end of the sentence, and sometimes he switches up clauses, but it's really not as exaggerated as the memes portray, lol.

But I do want to design that lemon t-shirt now. xD
